-= AutoEbooks =-
A simple Twitter "ebooks" app. 
Features:
 - unattended mode (automatic_mode in configs) â€” specially for scheduling in cron!
 - username != twittername, any timeline can be grabbed
 - remove t.co links and @mentions
 - OAuth login, asks you to go to a link and enter PIN on first launch, saves them in files
 - Optional BadTranslation via BING

Install dependencies by CDing into each folder of dependencies_archives and doing:
	python ./setup.py install
	
Edit markov_twit.py Settings section

Then run in the folder:
	python markov_twit.py
	
	
That is it!
Thanks for using AutoEbooks by vladkorotnev!
